West Bengal
Sep 03, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Human Trafficking, Rape
Description:
			A minor girl, who was brought into sex trade on false assurance of job, was today rescused by the police.

A minor girl of Baguihati area of North 24 Parganas district, was brought to a red light area of Kolkata on false assurances of a job a few days back, the police said.

Nakul Saha, who had known the girl for quite a few months promised her a job and then sold her to Bapi Pal of Dum Dum area.


